-- ── GSW tower, layer 2: substitution commutes with output weakening ───────────
-- weaken_n_commute: the two SemCtx_d weakenings — insert-at-0 (weaken_semctx_d)
--   and insert-at-cutoff-(succ n) (weaken_semctx_d_n) — commute on an environment.
