-- GSW: substituting into a weakened target context = weakening the substitution.
--   sub_open g t e (ins a n d) (weaken_semctx_d_n a d n g env)
--     = wk a d t (sub_open g t e d env) n
--   Cutoff-generalised (n) so the binder cases can fire the IH at (succ n).
